Hydras:

"Then, little, Maxima" said the male "Do you still want to come back 
the Autobots?"


--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, EmprzAnastazia@a... wrote:
> In a message dated 2/23/03 1:28:30 PM Central Standard Time, 
> airly2002@h... writes:
> 
> 
> > "Well when I called Rodimus Prime friend was an Iriony... " 
replied 
> > Hydras
> 
> Her optics upon him, watching him. She wouldn't drive the nail 
further on 
> this one. It made no sense to her. Only time she allied with 
Autobots is when 
> it was against the Quints... even Unicron on that fateful day. 
Nothing more. 
> She despised the Autobots. Hating them with a passion, loathing 
them. Never 
> forgiving them for what they had done. 
> 
> "Very well," stated so dry that it could be mistaken as annoyance. 
> 
> Time for a change of subject. She still had time to spare. Leaving 
this base &
>  returning to Wheeljack & the others would still be a bad choice. 
A major 
> mistake at that one. 
> 
> She stood there, silently. Watching him, waiting to see what would 
happen 
> next. Then her optics went to the bot. But her attention was still 
on Hydras.
